description.content:
Please contact me before placing an order to discuss availability.


Hey there! I'm Kaleem, a software engineer turned Webflow developer. With 6 years in the game, I've developed over 200 pixel-perfect, SEO-friendly, lightning-fast, and bug-free Webflow websites (as attested by 170+ 5 star reviews below). I stand by my work with a 100% money-back guarantee - I'm confident you'll be totally satisfied!


The services offered in this Gig:


  • Designing in Figma and then developing it in Webflow
  • Developing your Figma design or existing site in Webflow with 100% precision and attention to detail.
  • Making the website fluid responsive across all Desktop, Tablet and mobile devices.
  • Setting up Webflow CMS to make content management easy for you.
  • Adding Interactions & Animations site-wide to make the website pop.
  • Developing custom JavaScript, CSS & HTML code to surpass the limitations of Webflow.
  • Compressing all assets for speed.
  • Integrating 3rd party services and API's like Mailchimp, Zappier, GDPR popup etc.
  • Unlimited revisions until 100% satisfaction.


What's needed to get started?


  1. Your specs document OR figma design


Need a custom Quote? Contact me now.


﻿Peace ️️️️

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why should I hire YOU?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Choose me if you want peace of mind, if you want to be certain that the work delivered is of top quality with extreme attention to detail without doing 50 revisions. I've developed 300+ projects in Webflow in last 6 years so I know what exact business I'm in.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What exactly you do?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I take a high fidelity design in figma, xd or sketch and convert it into a live webflow website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you do custom Javascript programming as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can do custom Javascript programming to do things which are usually not possible with Webflow's native functionality, for example CMS slider.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you design the website as well
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, however, if design services are also required, there will be separate charges. This gig only includes development.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Where do you develop the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I'll develop the website in my account and transfer it to your account of completion, or I can develop it directly in your own account.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you create animations and interactions too?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can develop animations and interactions of any complexity, even if they require custom coding.
